### ==================== 订单模块 — 创建订单 ====================

### 变量：登录获取token后替换
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...

### 1. 正常创建订单
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 2. 收货人为空（参数校验失败）
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 3. 电话格式不正确
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "12345",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 4. 城市为空
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 5. 详细地址为空
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": ""
}

### 6. 购物车无选中商品（业务异常）
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 7. 未登录（Token过期或无效）
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 8. Token格式错误
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 9. 边界值 — 电话号码11位合法
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "李四",
  "telephone": "13912345678",
  "city": "上海",
  "address": "南京路200号"
}
